---
title: Quinoa Stuffed Peppers with Feta, Mushrooms, and Pepitas
description: Guess what? Quinoa isn’t actually a grain at all! In fact, it’s botanically related to spinach and beets. We love cooking with this ancient Incan superfood because it’s nutritious, hearty, and pairs well with so many flavors—especially the tangy ones in our stuffed peppers.
